'''''House of Gold''''' (yasohotse nka '''''Family Runs''''' kuri DVD) ni filime yo gusetsa yo muri [[Gana]] yo muri [[Nijeriya]] 2013, yakozwe na Yvonne Nelson ikayoborwa na Pascal Amanfo. Irimo Majid Michel, Yvonne Nelson, Omawumi Megbele, Mercy Chinwo, Ice Prince Zamani, Eddie Watson na Francis Odega .    

Iyi filime ivuga amateka y’umucuruzi w’umucuruzi ukunda gusabana , Dan Ansah Williams upfa azize kanseri kandi yabwiwe ko asigaje ibyumweru bitandatu ngo abeho. Afata icyemezo abifashijwemo n’avoka we guhamagara abana be bose basubira mu rugo, abenshi muri bo bakaba baravutse batashyingiranywe ndetse n’ibintu bitandukanye bitemewe. Ubumwe bwongeye kuzunguruka ibintu byinshi bitunguranye nkuko buri mwana agarutse afite gahunda, itanga ibisubizo bisekeje.

Yasohotse ku ya 12 Mata 2013 muri [[Gana]] no ku ya 19 Nyakanga 2013 muri [[Nijeriya]]. Nubwo iyi filime yagiye ihura n’ibitekerezo bitari byiza, yakiriye ibihembo muri Golden Icons Academy Movie Awards 2013, 2013 Gana Movie Awards, 2014 Africa Magic Viewers Choice Awards na 2013 Zulu African Film Academy Awards . Yatsindiye ibihembo bitandatu kuri icya nyuma, harimo ibyiciro: "Ishusho nziza", "Umuyobozi mwiza", "Umukinnyi witwaye neza", "Umukinnyi witwaye neza" na "Sinema nziza".

