== Kurekura ==
Inzu yamamaza ''Inzu ya Zahabu'' yasohotse kuri YouTube ku ya 4 Werurwe 2013.  Iyi filime yerekanwe bwa mbere muri [[Gana]] ku ya 12 Mata 2013  no muri [[Nijeriya]] ku ya 19 Nyakanga 2013,  mbere yo kujya ahagaragara muri rusange muri [[Nijeriya]].   Yasohotse kuri DVD ifite umutwe wa ''Family Runs'' mu Gushyingo 2013 na Henrikesim Multimedia Concept.
